Package: cowfootR
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Estimate the Carbon Footprint of Dairy Farms
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Juan", "Moreno", email = "juan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate the carbon footprint of dairy farms, based on IDF and IPCC
             methodologies. Includes tools for single-farm and batch analysis, report generation, and visualization.
